item.title: Need help with two things
item.dc:creator: @ledgman ledgman
item.description:
@ledgman wrote:

Open up player.java, search for

 public int q1

Then you will see all the quests with either nothing next to them or = 0.

Change all the quests to this…

 public int q1 = 15;

Basically just add = 15 to the end of it and remember to keep the ; at the end.

Also your second question… Encryption is there for a reason it’s to protect you incase your server somehow gets out into the open.
However you can remove it but i suggest not to.
